Title: Fix show mode in filter popup
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1617787749
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

If show mode was set to "Default to show more" or "Enforce show more mode" the
filters declared as "show more" were not shown in the filter popup within "Add
filter".
